Class DistributedDicomReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.marcolotz.lung.io.inputFormat.DistributedDicomReader

  • public class DistributedDicomReader
extends java.lang.Object
    DICOM specialized format reader. Reads the image data and also the metadata inside the DICOM image. It is a variation of the DicomReader class, without verbose and with a different constructor.
    Author:
    Marco Aurelio Lotz
